{"tid":2036611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"非洲排華潮開始　贊比亞3華人贊比亞遭搶劫殺害","createTime":"2020-05-26T14:28:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T13:29:32.000Z","uid":28114,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"52e944d14769d1e9724c0f76816e6ec9a364c24b","tid":2036611,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://maddog.myradio.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E6%8E%92%E8%8F%AF%E6%BD%AE%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B-%E8%B4%8A%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9E3%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B7%A5%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%AE%BA-1-1024x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaddog.myradio.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E6%258E%2592%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%25BD%25AE%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25A7%258B-%25E8%25B4%258A%25E6%25AF%2594%25E4%25BA%259E3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AE%25BA-1-1024x576.jpg&h=f348529d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【癲狗日報專訊】源於中國的武漢肺炎疫情在全球不斷蔓延，連非州多國都不能倖免，早前更有大批非裔人士在中國廣州遭受歧視，更引發尼日利亞與中國的外交風波。目前非洲疑出現反華情緒，東非國家贊比亞首都盧薩卡前日（廿四）更出現一宗針對攻擊中國人搶劫事件，至少三名中國商人遇害，還被燒屍洩憤。<br />\n據中國駐贊比亞大使館官方網站的聲明指，事件發生在24日中午盧薩卡市一間中國公司倉庫，3名中國公民遇害。中國駐當地大使已經向外長提出嚴正交涉，強烈譴責惡性暴力事件，強烈要求當地警方盡早破案，依法嚴懲兇犯，並敦促贊比亞採取有效措施，切實維護當地中國公民生命財產安全和正當合法權益。<br />\n當地警方表示，疑犯為2男1女，進入倉庫後，殺害並搶劫3名中國人，並縱火企圖毁滅證據。當地警方現拘捕2名男疑犯，正追捕另一名在逃女疑犯。<br />\n截至2020年5月24日為止，贊比亞當地錄得832宗武漢肺炎累計確診個案，其中7人死亡。但有學者指，非洲各國醫療水平惡劣，大批患者沒辦法進行病毒測試，相信非洲各國感染數字可能更為嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://maddog.myradio.hk/2020/05/26/newsdesk/international/非洲排華潮開始-贊比亞3華人贊比亞遭搶劫殺害/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaddog.myradio.hk%2F2020%2F05%2F26%2Fnewsdesk%2Finternational%2F%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E6%8E%92%E8%8F%AF%E6%BD%AE%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B-%E8%B4%8A%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9E3%E8%8F%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%B4%8A%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9E%E9%81%AD%E6%90%B6%E5%8A%AB%E6%AE%BA%E5%AE%B3%2F&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA9ey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=62c426e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://maddog.myradio.hk/2020/05/26/newsdesk/international/非洲排華潮開始-贊比亞3華人贊比亞遭搶劫殺害/</a>"},{"pid":"5f19f05ad4156d1623d38772bc60c6a5d554c90a","tid":2036611,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:32:19.000Z","msg":"得3個 only"},{"pid":"9e999b4f5dacfb854e04b11500388d3e7793bab4","tid":2036611,"uid":171313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da7c0d136d34049a752febcf2e4cd4d99a7bde4","tid":2036611,"uid":28759,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:22:21.000Z","msg":"中国公民<br />\n冇殺錯就 OK <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed596318c823530ef0d8fc4a276fcd756a735aa5","tid":2036611,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:36:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">贊比亞手足做得好</span></span>"},{"pid":"d335c78e4f9d0b5598a1e0e9986325befaeca55e","tid":2036611,"uid":37528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:37:43.000Z","msg":"贊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db97bb043e028fe938801b7d0b5f0050c98b50b","tid":2036611,"uid":99828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:38:15.000Z","msg":"13億個thanks"},{"pid":"788286f73b49bf9fd70932825848043f1ec8f40f","tid":2036611,"uid":103976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T15:40:21.000Z","msg":"非洲手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e43193bbdcd0745e1c47b11f211d3fb05255